      "id": "PopularPost107409",
      "post_content": "Using this, some [Memory Crystal](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Memory Crystal)s, a few [Mana Flare](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mana Flare)s, and a [Searing Touch](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Searing Touch), I created an infinite damage combo. One mountain with three Mana Flares gives RRRR. R to cast Searing touch, Buyback for 0 thanks to the Memory Crystals, then the remaining RRR are used to activate the Talisman to untap the Mountain. ",
