      "id": "PopularPost317289",
      "post_content": "I think this card's ability should be changed from triggered to activated (as printed), because now it can't be countered by things like [Voidmage Husher](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Voidmage Husher) or [Squelch](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Squelch).  \n[Nacre Talisman](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nacre Talisman), [Lapis Lazuli Talisman](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lapis Lazuli Talisman), [Onyx Talisman](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Onyx Talisman) and [Malachite Talisman](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Malachite Talisman) should be changed as well.",
      "posted_by": "LCD88",
